"default": "Hello researcher, you have been sent on an important mission in the deepest parts of the Mariana Trench to locate and photograph various unidentified objects/creatures. You have only a coordinate system to guide you on your expedition. Make sure to keep an eye on your equipment, as malfunctions may occur. Good luck out there, and try not to die.",
